reviews.text: Another amazing cocktail bar. It rivals ones I've been to in Shanghai, Tokyo and San Francisco. Wonderful bartenders who can make anything your heart desires. The atmosphere is superb and the prices are very reasonable. Will be back here next time I am in Hong Kong.

Very nice Japanese 'speakeasy' style cocktail / whiskey bar. The service of the bartenders was faultless, with all the theatre and pomp that goes with a great cocktail experience. I did find it quite expensive; we only had a drink each which didn't reach the minimum spend so there was an additional charged added to the bill to cover it.
Imaginative and impeccably executed seasonal fruit cocktails! Service is excellent too.

Highly entertaining, educational, and a great way to try new cocktails until inebriation :). Barkeeps are first rate... give them some flavors and what you like or want to avoid and voila it’s night night time :)
Excellent service! Creative cocktails! No other place could compare with! You dont need a menu. Just tell them what you like and they will do the rest.

result.formatted_address: 7/F, 麼地大廈, Mody House, No. 30 Mody Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui, 香港
result.name: Bar Buonasera

reviews.text:
一間日式酒吧，店內地方比較小位置都不多，所以建議上去飲既時候要提早1-2日打電話預約。 一入店內職員即遞上熱毛巾同冰水，服務質素豪無疑問係一流。到酒方面，第一杯我叫左Manhattan，酒一上黎 已經係聞到陣陣既香味，飲落口即刻滿足到我呢種咁鐘意飲重酒味既人🥃。飲呢杯酒個種爆炸既感覺真係路識形容😋。
另外小食方面叫左和牛串燒同埋burger with fries，和牛配上蔥同埋菇又係冇得輸系列。至於burger 都有驚喜，入面塊肉煎出黎有肉汁 非常新鮮美味。薯條方面都睇到佢地既細心位，每條薯條都沾上磨得幼細既鹽同黑椒粉，食落口唔會影響口感。
總合以上，服務、食物同埋酒都係非常出色，強烈建議要入去Chill。呢間咁出色既酒吧 我會再繼續去！！！

Another amazing cocktail bar. It rivals ones I've been to in Shanghai, Tokyo and San Francisco. Wonderful bartenders who can make anything your heart desires. The atmosphere is superb and the prices are very reasonable. Will be back here next time I am in Hong Kong.

低消要200元港幣的Bar，連點餐都需要用英文溝通才比較順利！若坐在吧台邊感覺一定會更棒～
聽女友說調酒好喝，我個人則覺得炸物好吃！

有位講廣東話的服務人員很親切，為不喝酒的我特調了一杯綠色的芒果特調！

Very nice Japanese 'speakeasy' style cocktail / whiskey bar. The service of the bartenders was faultless, with all the theatre and pomp that goes with a great cocktail experience. I did find it quite expensive; we only had a drink each which didn't reach the minimum spend so there was an additional charged added to the bill to cover it.

日本人の女性のバーテンさんがいます。
気さくな方でした。
他のスタッフも良い感じです。
寄ってみてはどうでしょう。
勿論、美味しかったです。　丁寧です。
